> the risk of overflowing the actual gadget.

Can`t see any other way to predict the size, the way you do it is fool proof as it 
will at least not write beyond the gadget. Mui gadgets also look like this often, 
lots of space and little text, you can`t have it all ;-) Live with it I`d say.

