It's not a limitation of MUI. There are a couple of flags that can be set in MUI
which force resizing of the gadget to the length of the text. eg.

MUISet obj,#MUIA_Text_SetMin,True,#MUIA_Text_SetMax,True

would ensure that your gadget is always the same size as the text it contains.

