Maybe you don't have an active entry?

Also, by taking &gl you are getting the address of the start of the string, not the 
address of the string pointer. You probably need to do something like this:

DefType.l gl
item.l=muiget(list,#MUIA_List_GetEntry_Active)
MuiDoMethod 2,#MUIA_List_GetEntry,item,&gl
If gl<>0
    NPrint Peek$(gl)
